# VHS demo for snap/datepicker — regenerate with:  vhs datepicker/demo.tape
# (run from the snap repo root; gif output is a build artifact, not diffable)
Output datepicker/demo.gif
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 700
Set Height 480
Set TypingSpeed 60ms
Type "go run ./examples/datepicker"
Enter
Sleep 3s
Right
Sleep 500ms
Right
Sleep 500ms
Down
Sleep 500ms
Down
Sleep 1s
Enter
Sleep 1500ms
